---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | AuthLayer"
  description="Privacy policy for AuthLayer — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="privacy-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <span class="tag">Legal</span>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="meta">Last updated: June 1, 2025</p>
      </header>

      <div class="policy-body">
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>AuthLayer</strong> ("we", "us", or "our") collects,
          uses, and shares information when you visit <a href="https://authlayer.dev">authlayer.dev</a> (the "Site").
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We do not require registration or account creation to read content on AuthLayer. When you
          visit the Site, standard server and analytics data may be collected automatically, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
          <li>Referring URL</li>
          <li>Device type and operating system</li>
          <li>IP address (anonymised)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          The Site uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to operate and improve your experience.
          These include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — We use Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand how
            visitors use the Site. This service may collect anonymised usage data.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Advertising cookies</strong> — We use Google AdSense to display advertisements.
            Google may use cookies to personalise ads based on your prior visits to this site and
            other sites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve
            ads based on your visit to AuthLayer and other sites on the Internet.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You may opt out of personalised advertising by visiting
          <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Google Ads Settings
          </a>
          or by visiting
          <a href="http://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            aboutads.info
          </a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Google AdSense</h2>
        <p>
          We use Google AdSense, a third-party advertising service provided by Google LLC. Google
          AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to this website or other
          websites. Google's advertising requirements can be summed up by
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Google's Advertising Principles
          </a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits to
          our site. For more information on how Google collects and processes data in connection with
          advertising, see
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Google's Privacy Policy
          </a>.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Operate and improve the Site</li>
          <li>Understand how visitors use our content</li>
          <li>Display relevant advertisements</li>
          <li>Diagnose technical problems</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Articles on AuthLayer may link to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the
          privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain anonymised analytics data for up to 12 months. We do not store personal
          information beyond what is necessary to operate the Site.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on your location, you may have rights under applicable privacy law (such as
          GDPR or CCPA) to access, correct, or delete personal data we hold about you. To exercise
          these rights, contact us at the address below.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top
          of this page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the Site after changes
          constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:khashayar.parhami@gmail.com">khashayar.parhami@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-page { padding: 3rem 0 5rem; }

  .page-header { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .page-header .tag { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .meta { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; }

  .policy-body { max-width: 720px; }

  .policy-body p { color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.75; }

  .policy-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .policy-body ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .policy-body li {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .policy-body li::before {
    content: '–';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .policy-body strong { color: var(--text); }
  .policy-body a { color: var(--accent); text-underline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
